-- APA Group May Bid For Alinta Energy's Power Assets, Financial Review Says
-- Sarah McDonald
-- 2010-06-28T21:34:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/apa-group-may-bid-for-alinta-energy-s-power-assets-financial-review-says.html

          
          
             APA Group is considering bidding for
some of Alinta Energy Ltd.’s assets, the Australian Financial
Review reported, citing an interview with APA Managing Director
Mick McCormack. APA may look at Alinta’s gas transmission,
distribution and gas-fired power generation assets, the
newspaper cited McCormack as saying. The company may also be
interested in increasing its stake in Envestra Ltd., McCormack
said, according to the Review.  
